{"tid":1327731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【721戰術】掟野冇用架！有啲野係唔work就唔work。","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:29:54.000Z","uid":223260,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1e71682d1d878ac6d0dcf718c9e2dfc5dbcac3","tid":1327731,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次嘅主題係話俾大家聽創意要合乎現實，有啲野係唔work就唔work，<span style=\"color: orange;\">啓迪思考</span>。<br />\n<br />\n本post乃係警戒世人，放下屠刀立地成佛做良好公民，切勿以身試法，<span style=\"color: orange;\">並無任何明示或暗示公衆作出非法行爲之意</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之一：掟一件野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n話知你喺屋企開發咗件咩驚天地泣鬼神嘅驅狗法寶出黎，掟一件野一啲用都冇，咁樣只會俾新聞報你升咗級，但係唔會有升級嘅效果。只會攞黎衰。除非閣下精準度如死神來了，一擊命中要害。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之二：掟兩件野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果閣下開發咗件要兩件同時命中同一個目標先會生效嘅法寶，對唔住都係冇用。混亂情況下冇可能同時中一個目標兩次。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之三：喺屋企砌好啲野攞出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n已經有好多位義士出過事，閣下唔可能帶住件法寶<span style=\"color: red;\">着住黑衫黑褲額頭刻住暴徒</span>兩隻字走出黎搭車出銅鑼灣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之四：掟完就算</span></span><br />\n<br />\n部分義士有時可能誤以爲自己帶咗粒核彈出街，一粒就搞掂，唔需要後續行動。除非你掟嘅野真係好勁好勁，唔係單靠掟件野唔會有用。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之五：冇補給</span></span><br />\n<br />\n平時FPS故事模式，大家都會做咩？越稀有、用途越狹窄就越難補給。我記得某個post有個好可愛嘅絲打話要用鈉對付水炮車，因爲鈉加水會生火，大家唔好學佢咁可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔work之六：傷害性氣體、液體</span></span><br />\n<br />\n氣體好快消散，液體好易稀釋，警用催淚彈係大廠出，你唔會做到。除非你用貨車運大量過黎咁癡線咁我冇野好講。<br />\n<br />\n最後，綜合上述唔work嘅原因，秉承在下和平理性優雅非暴力非粗口嘅原則，奉勸各位和平示威，<span style=\"color: orange;\">廣泛討論</span>，唔好掟野。"},{"pid":"61f4863960fc7d62f1fc0e50529fdf77579d739b","tid":1327731,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】</strong></span><br />\n光復香港！沒有暴民，只有暴政！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=79fdc926\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割蓆 不篤灰 不分化 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n七大訴求<br />\n - 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n - 永久完全撤回逃犯條<br />\n - 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n - 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n - 撤回暴動定性<br />\n - 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n - 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327503/page/1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1326334/page/1</a></span>"},{"pid":"dbffeb3d779fee077758f3d76a283354bd2dd697","tid":1327731,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb867c47a8f36227bc4f60c344a5eb2fa7baf65","tid":1327731,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:06:53.000Z","msg":"根據樓主意見<br />\n<br />\n佢教大家要搵啲丟幾粒就極大殺傷既武器<br />\n<br />\n同埋一種海量、易量產既便於携帶投擲型武器"},{"pid":"4c967d7818b050686d2621318b0ec38c202bf268","tid":1327731,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efb867c47a8f36227bc4f60c344a5eb2fa7baf65","tid":1327731,"uid"